I identified the highest-leverage gap: `latest:core:full_response` keeps chaining from the most recent run even when an earlier run has equal benchmark stability but better generalization. I’m implementing one narrow resolver improvement so Stage-2 can pick the best completed parent run by benchmark stability first, then validation loss, then recency.
